# Env
.env
.env.local

# Secrets — defensive catch-alls. The real user config lives at
# %APPDATA%\Harvester\config.json (outside the repo) and is never tracked,
# but these patterns keep any stray copies from ever landing in git.
**/config.json
!tsconfig*.json
!package.json
!package-lock.json
*.env.*
*.secret
*.secrets
secrets.*
*.pem
*.key
credentials.json
